<br>
I want to thank everyone who helped me get my Firey Avenger!  It was a long and hard quest and I thank the help from everyone involved.  Even though we could not do the dragon raids as a guild, many of you came and saw the luck of my dice.  Thanks to FoJ for helping with the Lich of Miragul and to all my fellow guildies.  Lastly, Thanks to Emmuar and a special thanks to Javerx from Azure Legion the resident PoA necro who made the final turn in possible.<br>
<br>
I also want to clear up the fact that this weapon is not my final epic (Pallys have four such swords), but by all accounts this is the hardest one to acquire in the chain of events that leads to my final Epic sword, the Firey Defender.<br>
<br>
All in all, I have been extremely lucky (well I think I did play one solid week of pure dragon raids) but I know there are others that have worked harder than myself.  I will try to be as humble as possible regarding this issue.  WOOT I GOT IT....err sorry.<br>
<br>
For all non-Pally memebers who are curious here are the stats:<br>
<br>
2hs Dmg 33, Dly 44.  15 Str  15 Wis  10 Cha  5 vsMg  5 vsFire  5 vsCold  5 vsPos  5 vsDis  25 HP  25 Mana  0.10 Wt  Effect Flame Shock (110hp DD) and the special bonus of 2 Hand Bash!<br>
<br>
There will be a special roll for my current ToY at our next guild raid. Need only.<br>
<br>
Hikmer Hefeweizen<br>
52nd Cavalier of the Blackburrow Stout Co.<br>
